body: |- wceq(cstrkgcb, cab(s0, wsbc(s1, cfv(cbs, cv(s0)), wsbc(s2, cfv(cds, cv(s0)), wsbc(s3, cfv(citv, cv(s0)), wa(wral(s4, cv(s1), wral(s5, cv(s1), wral(s6, cv(s1), wral(s7, cv(s1), wral(s8, cv(s1), wral(s9, cv(s1), wral(s10, cv(s1), wral(s11, cv(s1), wi(wa(w3a(wne(cv(s4), cv(s5)), wcel(cv(s5), co(cv(s4), cv(s3), cv(s6))), wcel(cv(s9), co(cv(s8), cv(s3), cv(s10)))), wa(wa(wceq(co(cv(s4), cv(s2), cv(s5)), co(cv(s8), cv(s2), cv(s9))), wceq(co(cv(s5), cv(s2), cv(s6)), co(cv(s9), cv(s2), cv(s10)))), wa(wceq(co(cv(s4), cv(s2), cv(s7)), co(cv(s8), cv(s2), cv(s11))), wceq(co(cv(s5), cv(s2), cv(s7)), co(cv(s9), cv(s2), cv(s11)))))), wceq(co(cv(s6), cv(s2), cv(s7)), co(cv(s10), cv(s2), cv(s11)))))))))))), wral(s4, cv(s1), wral(s5, cv(s1), wral(s8, cv(s1), wral(s9, cv(s1), wrex(s6, cv(s1), wa(wcel(cv(s5), co(cv(s4), cv(s3), cv(s6))), wceq(co(cv(s5), cv(s2), cv(s6)), co(cv(s8), cv(s2), cv(s9)))))))))))))))
comment: Define the class of geometries fulfilling the five segment axiom, Axiom A5 of [Schwabhauser] p. 11, and segment construction axiom, Axiom A4 of [Schwabhauser] p. 11. (Contributed by Thierry Arnoux, 14-Mar-2019.)
